channel.title: Runescape Remake! [F2P]
channel.description:
[center] [img]http://i301.photobucket.com/albums/nn72/localwoodcut/f2premake.jpg[/img]
[u][b]Runescape F2P Remake source![/b][/u]
Before we continue, this source is not completed, I do intend to complete, however. There is currently, what cannot be called an anti leach, eh.. A time consumer. :)
There is one too many/less brace in Client.java add/remove it in the right place to fix the source. Until then, you'll get 100 errors. ;)
[u][b]Features[/b][/u] Exp rate is the same as Runescape! [Can be modified easily] Members teleports will say "Please log in to a members server to use this teleport." 100% NPCS & Shops with correct items & stock for Varrock, Al-Kharid, Falador & Lumbridge. Dragon slayer quest 90% finished. Added more consumable food, Including jug of wine/half jug of wine, Pizza/half pizza, 3-piece cake, tuna, salmon, trout, swordfish, shrimp & bread. Removed any access to P2P shops/items/areas Made a lot of doors open, including, but not limited to, Champions guild, Oziach's hut, Goblin hut, Al Kharid Toll Gate, And Lumbridge church. You need to complete dragon slayer to be able to wear rune platebody And some other varieties.
[b]I DO PLAN TO FINISH THIS SOURCE, IT HAS VERY FEW FEATURES AT THE MOMENT. Any client is supported, since the source has F2P only items, and no custom maps, so moparscape client would also be supported![/b]
[b]Link[/b]: http://www.mediafire.com/?mjyyz5jnbjm
[u][b]Screenshots[/b][/u] [IMG]http://i301.photobucket.com/albums/nn72/localwoodcut/pic7.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i301.photobucket.com/albums/nn72/localwoodcut/pic2.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i301.photobucket.com/albums/nn72/localwoodcut/pic5.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i301.photobucket.com/albums/nn72/localwoodcut/pic3.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i301.photobucket.com/albums/nn72/localwoodcut/pic4.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i301.photobucket.com/albums/nn72/localwoodcut/pic6.jpg[/img]
[b]Credits[/b] Jagex - Original F2P Runescape 2005 & Inspiration. Delta - Deltascape Base. The Unholy - For the aforementioned features. [/center]
